. Tyson and he's been great. If you're an older male on TRT and are still feeling exhausted and tired of the low dosages dictated by your insurance company and conservative thinking doctor, I strongly advise you call PRC today! You won't regret it.","textLang":"en","relativePublishTimeDescription":"2 months ago","publishTime":"2026-02-04T21:08:43.921801361Z","authorName":"Rich Stachura","authorUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112506201279181772573/reviews","authorPhotoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIodYHTC1Qqgdu7B6E7LifGkK2hwwuLXBi0tB9vU7CVvHmobQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},{"name":"places/ChIJQWPlIYPIt4kRIGFYKwcqywo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pJdGMwcDBhMDQ1YVZkQmVrUTBaMlZGTmtaSVFuYxAB","rating":5,"text":"PRC has been amazingly professional and responsive for years, consistently unwavering. I actually trust them more than most doctors' offices. They have caught things in my labs that my Primary Care Physician missed, and they provided me with multiple robust, holistic, and comprehensive plans and recommendations to bring me back to optimal health.","textLang":"en","relativePublishTimeDescription":"6 months ago","publishTime":"2025-09-24T15:07:19.371331199Z","authorName":"Tahj Merriman","authorUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113343816924171886088/reviews","authorPhotoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkyiRpbWY2OcSDI7Bx308LZrLS7-_CsVHNXrvgu7U6X8CGFdRQ=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},{"name":"places/ChIJQWPlIYPIt4kRIGFYKwcqywo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25KV01XWmhMVmhMUkhSQlJtMTNSRWhTYTNWWFRtYxAB","rating":5,"text":"Great experience across the board. Holistically examined my treatment and I felt comfortable during each step, I've been seeing Dr. Tyson for years and he has always kept me in great shape through examination of my total health. Highly recommend.\nMike as the care coordinator is always available to help and quick to respond and assist with any issue or concern.  Great team all around.","textLang":"en","relativePublishTimeDescription":"8 months ago","publishTime":"2025-08-12T14:56:38.198868498Z","authorName":"William Vickery","authorUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111297874545477842264/reviews","authorPhotoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJicOzliVjKQamgSkRVwlXEM-YmHhFsC-amkRp5Fq2sp1_U0A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"},{"name":"places/ChIJQWPlIYPIt4kRIGFYKwcqywo/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t0cmFUbHVibWRtVGtaWU5IazFZMUJHTFV4MWFVRRAB","rating":1,"text":"Owner was rude, impatient, and arrogant on the phone when asked simple medical and financial questions. Glad I did my research first!\n\nCompetitors who offer same services faster and at cheaper prices:\n\n1) HydraMed — peptides sent to your door for one flat fee. Their peptide prices are several hundred dollars cheaper and don't require lab tasting or tele-health visits.\n2) EvolveTelemed — peptides are several hundred dollars cheaper. Monthly memberships range from $25/month to $149/month depending on what you are looking for.\n3) Viome — $299 for a full-body intelligence test. Done from your home. I have already purchased this and am very pleased with the whole experience. They also provide supplement subscriptions based on your test results.\n\nMy experience with Performance Rejuvenation Center:\n\nI spoke to a man on the phone who identified himself as Eric and said he was the new owner of the clinic. He had a bad attitude and gave disrespectful/unprofessional responses like \"oh my god\" when I asked him basic questions. It seemed that he just wanted to get me into the clinic and have me pay without answering questions first. I was very uncomfortable throughout the duration of the call.\n\nAgain, I simply asked basic medical and financial questions. I thought he was an AI call agent at first since he also kept cutting me off during my questions. There were even times I got only one or two words in (I am not exaggerating) and he immediately responded, which didn’t answer my question since he didn’t let me finish it.\n\nI would recommend checking out the companies I mentioned above. The people on the phone were very helpful, knowledgeable, and respectful. Not to mention, their services are better priced and have a quicker turnaround time, which is why I am very glad I called around and did my research first. After finding so many better options, it is clear why Eric was so quick to dismiss my phone call.\n\nUpdate to owner’s response:\nHe is lying, don’t fall for it. This text below is directly from Hydramed’s FAQ page: “HydraMed ensures the highest level of quality and safety by partnering with 503A compounding pharmacies for HydraMed RX and 503B outsourcing facilities for HydraMed IV therapy products. These pharmacies meet stringent FDA compliance requirements, including regular inspections, and rigorously follow state and federal regulations. Many of our pharmacy partners go beyond standard requirements by achieving additional certifications, such as LegitScript Certification, National Association of Boards of Pharmacy (NABP) Accreditation, and PCAB Accreditation.”\n\nNowhere on their page did I see the words “for research purposes only” on the peptides I was looking to purchase.\n\nHydramed is a bigger, better established business with offices in 29 major cities across the United States. They have been featured on multiple news channels and over 500 websites. I wish I had found them first so I didn’t have to waste my time with this business and its rude owner. As I have said, there are better options out there that are FDA approved, such as Hydramed. If you ask too many questions that expose his pricey business model, Eric will likely label you a “liability” as well without giving any specifics.","textLang":"en","relativePublishTimeDescription":"7 months ago","publishTime":"2025-08-31T18:09:50.959209208Z","authorName":"Haydenn","authorUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112446872352452949825/reviews","authorPhotoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdHCM0L8Oc32f1yGK2LwnQlATrWLTObnpwpzbrd-n1rfSffAOcUA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"},{"name":"places/ChIJQWPlIYPIt4kRIGFYKwcqywo/reviews/ChRDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTURneWVwdhAB","rating":5,"text":"I've been working with PRC for years with great results.   At my age, extra weight becomes a real challenge.   Dr. Tyson took my medical information and personal goals and pointed me in the right direction quickly.  I'm already seeing results and feel great about my treatment!","textLang":"en","relativePublishTimeDescription":"a year ago","publishTime":"2025-02-25T18:01:31.666478Z","authorName":"Jeff Kearns","authorUri":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115041616001666437213/reviews","authorPhotoUri":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJHn00O_5KxTNMW_bYpzwwAfwO2phiOajl_F-J3_BVnOKb_3g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}],"accessibility":{"wheelchairAccessibleParking":true,"wheelchairAccessibleEntrance":true},"payment":{"acceptsCreditCards":true,"acceptsDebitCards":true,"acceptsCashOnly":false},"extrasEnrichedAt":"2026-04-22T14:47:01Z"},{"placeId":"ChIJDTGL2J-3t4kR_i8XayezkVU","name":"Renew Vitality Testosterone Clinic of Washington DC","slug":"renew-vitality-testosterone-clinic-of-washington-dc","address":"1724 20th St NW STE 3, Washington, DC 20009","street":null,"city":"Washington","citySlug":"washington","state":"DC","stateSlug":"district-of-columbia","zip":"20009","lat":38.91361260000001,"lng":-77.0450451,"phone":"(202) 888-3055","website":"https://www.vitalityhrt.com/location/testosterone-clinic-of-washington-dc/?utm_source=google&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=gmb&utm_term=vitalityhrt&utm_content=washington-dc","rating":5,"ratingCount":9,"priceLevel":null,"googleUrl":"https://maps.google.com/?cid=6165906346728697854&g_mp=Cidnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLlNlYXJjaFRleHQQAhgEIAA","hours":["Monday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Tuesday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Thursday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Friday: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM","Saturda